9/*
10 * This header file is constructed to match the version described by
11 * PCAP_VERSION_MAJ.
12 *
13 * The structure largely derives from libpcap which wouldn't include
14 * nicely without bpf.
15 */
16typedef struct pcap_filehdr {
17 u_int pc_id;
18 u_short pc_v_maj;
19 u_short pc_v_min;
20 u_int pc_zone;
21 u_int pc_sigfigs;
22 u_int pc_slen;
23 u_int pc_type;
24} pcaphdr_t;
25
26#define TCPDUMP_MAGIC 0xa1b2c3d4
27
28#define PCAP_VERSION_MAJ 2
29
30typedef struct pcap_pkthdr {
31 struct timeval ph_ts;
32 u_int ph_clen;
33 u_int ph_len;
34} pcappkt_t;
